_sText:
This is my ZombieMod-Map called zm_horror_hotel.
It includes many rooms in which you can hide.
There is also a teleport room which leads to other parts of the map.
And there is a generator-room with a button that shuts down the entire power system of the map, so it is completely dark.
This room is secured by button which has to be unlocked by a hidden button in the map.
